<!-- # Project Management API

A comprehensive project management API built with Node.js, TypeScript, MongoDB, and Redis. This API provides full functionality for managing projects, tasks, teams, and users with authentication, analytics, and real-time features.

## ЁЯЪА Features

- **User Management**: Registration, authentication, profile management
- **Project Management**: Create, update, delete, and manage projects
- **Task Management**: Full CRUD operations with status tracking, comments, and assignments
- **Team Management**: Create teams, manage members, and collaborate
- **Dashboard & Analytics**: Comprehensive analytics and reporting
- **Real-time Updates**: WebSocket support for real-time collaboration
- **Security**: JWT authentication, rate limiting, input validation
- **Caching**: Redis integration for improved performance
- **Email Integration**: Automated email notifications

## ЁЯЫая╕П Technology Stack

- **Runtime**: Node.js with TypeScript
- **Framework**: Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB with Mongoose ODM
- **Cache**: Redis
- **Authentication**: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- **Validation**: Joi schema validation
- **Security**: Helmet, CORS, Rate limiting
- **Documentation**: Auto-generated API docs

